GIVES SNOW SHOWERS TO THE NORTHEASTERN WATERS. A LOW 970 HPA WEST OF NEW
FOUNDLAND IS MOVING DEEPENING RAPIDLY TO TIMMIARMIUT AND GIVES HEAVY STRONG
